('piment_vegetarien_marine_guadeloupean', 'Piment végétarien mariné', 28, 1.5, 6.0, 0.3, 1.8, 3.5, 30, NULL, 'research', ARRAY['piment végétarien mariné', 'piment doux mariné', 'sweet chili pickle guadeloupe'], 'traditional', NULL, 1, 'GP', 'Marinated sweet chili peppers (piment végétarien), the non-hot local chili essential in all Guadeloupean cooking. These peppers have the aroma of scotch bonnet without the heat.', TRUE),
